<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="do-v">do <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /də:;du:/    美 /də:;du/  </p>
<p>(did, done)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>做；干；执行 (任务)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>do the / some / one’s cleaning / shopping / washing / cooking
扫除/购物/洗衣服/做饭</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>do one’s homework / housework
做家庭作业/干家务</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What is done cannot be undone.
覆水难收。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>行动；表现；进展：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m not accustomed to this, but I will try to do as you say. 
我还不习惯这样，但我会尽量按照你说的去做。</p><footer>2005 上海</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Vegetables do well here.
这里蔬菜长得很好。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>从事 (职业)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>What do you do</strong>?
你是做什么工作的？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What does he <strong>do for a living</strong>?
他做什么工作谋生？</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>学习；研究；解决：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m doing physics, biology and chemistry.
我在学习物理、生物和化学。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Are you good at doing crosswords?
你擅长填纵横字谜吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>度过：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She did a year backpacking around the world.
她用了一年时间背包旅行环游世界。</p></div>

<h4 id="6">6.<strong>适合；足够：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think pizza will do for lunch, don’t you?
我觉得午饭吃比萨就行，你觉得呢？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Can you lend me some money? 
你能借给我点钱吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Sure. will $20 do?
当然可以，20美元够吗？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-have-to-do-with">be / have to do with</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>关于；与……有关：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm sorry about the accident, but it is / has nothing to do with me.
对这次事故我感到很抱歉，但此事与我毫无关系。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How we understand things has a lot to do with what we feel.
我们如何理解事物与我们的感觉有很大关系。</p><footer>2015 北京</footer></div>

<h3 id="do-away-with">do away with</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>废除：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They did away with the law.
他们废除了那项法律。</p></div>

<h3 id="do-up">do up</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>包起来；捆；修缮；打扮：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do up a parcel.
捆包裹。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why don’t they clean up the river and do up that old house next to the bridge?
他们为什么不清理河道，并修缮桥边的那座老房子呢？</p><footer>北师大⑧ – 24</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She did herself up for the dinner.
她打扮起来参加宴会。</p></div>

<h3 id="do-with">do with</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>处置；（使）度过时间：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>David’s biggest headache is <strong>what to do with</strong> his money.
最让大卫头疼的是如何处置他的钱。</p><footer>2009 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She didn’t know <strong>what to do with</strong> herself after she retired.
退休后她不知道该怎么打发时间。</p></div>

<h3 id="do-without">do without</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>没有…也行；将就：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don’t have any sugar so you’ll have to do without.
我没有糖了，所以你只好将就一下。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>That’s why I help brighten people’s days. If you <strong><em>_</em></strong>, who’s to say that another person will?    （2015 湖南）<br />
A.didn’t <br />
B.don’t<br />
C.weren’t<br />
D. haven’t  </li>
<li>During the war there was a serious lack of food. It was not unusual that even the wealthy families had to do <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ bread for days.  （2009 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. B  2. without  </p></div>